{"tid":878330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港遲下都有死神之眼","createTime":"2018-10-27T04:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T05:23:55.000Z","uid":78533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dad74f4e5d125c021c128fa31ad2d52ac5830b23","tid":878330,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"見到隔離有個咁既POST~<br />\n<br />\n但唔好以為好搞笑 好快係你身邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為香港好快有<br />\n唔好以為係鳩吹 咩死神之眼 本身影晒相都好易認 <br />\n遲下轉埋身份証 經過眼仔即時顯示你資料 再記錄你著左咩色衫褲鞋 <br />\n再勁D就好似 以圖搜尋咁 連咩牌子都分到 <br />\n即時做個3D模擬你既樣 加合併埋影到你果到衫褲  想走都難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果D叮身份証既又係ON9 一影到你冇資料 你估黑警會點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n諗諗下仲勁過死神之眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要搵一個人 只要起多幾個接收站就得 <br />\n<br />\n唉 諗到呢到 好彩叫拎住個冇咩用既BNO 叫做好過班回歸後囉 其實玩到普教中都分唔到97後既係蝗定港架啦  大家自己小心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6963dce1e7554b15ccc4cf9655eef1cc76c26e89","tid":878330,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"如果香港IT咁先進既話,隔離班IT狗就唔洗比人炒啦"},{"pid":"f6f87f6c1631517116469238f0d7e49ed54d4360","tid":878330,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6963dce1e7554b15ccc4cf9655eef1cc76c26e89","tid":878330,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"如果香港IT咁先進既話,隔離班IT狗就唔洗比人炒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實就係基本技術都有 只係有冇人去完善"},{"pid":"fdadb00f618a6e53fc6a5d736d01b1ffa930bb40","tid":878330,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"Sell大陸單既保險雞要貼大字報日夜拷打"}]}